Payback;;69;;55;;R;;Porter (Mel Gibson) is a thief betrayed by both his wife, Lynn (Deborah Kara Unger), and his partner, Val (Gregg Henry), when he is shot in the back after a heist. Slowly, Porter recovers from his wounds and begins a search for Val, intent on recovering his share of the money they stole together. With the aid of prostitute Rosie (Maria Bello), Porter captures Val but still cannot find his cash. For this, Porter will have to challenge an imposing crime syndicate called the Outfit.;;Action,Mystery & thriller;;Brian Helgeland;;1999;;Mel Gibson,Gregg Henry,Maria Bello,Deborah Kara Unger,David Paymer,Bill Duke,Jack Conley,William Devane,Kris Kristofferson,John Glover,Lucy Liu,Sterling Wolfe,James Coburn;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1087648-payback